# 11. Risks

Potential risks include:

- Token bugs
- Session failures
- Expired verification links
- Misconfigured environment variables
- Email delivery failure
- Weak error handling
- Middleware bypass

Mitigation:

- Manual testing
- Security review
- End-to-end flow validation

